{"type":"message","id":"226f4e04","parentId":"b902b390","timestamp":"2026-06-09T06:10:52.003Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I will now create the posts and write them to the output file.\n<execute_ipython>\nimport json\n\nproject_url = \"https://coinography.com\"\nproject_name = \"Coinography\"\nniche = \"crypto discussions\"\n\nposts = [\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://www.kryptomoney.com/submit-guest-post\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"kryptomoney.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"The Future of Crypto: Navigating the Next Wave of Digital Assets\",\n      \"content\": f\"\"\"\nThe cryptocurrency landscape is in a constant state of flux. While Bitcoin and Ethereum continue to dominate headlines, a new wave of digital assets is quietly gaining momentum, promising to reshape the future of finance. For those of us deeply engaged in **crypto discussions**, it's a pivotal moment.\n\nOne of the most exciting developments is the rise of decentralized finance (DeFi) platforms that offer more than just trading. These platforms are building entire ecosystems of financial services, from lending and borrowing to insurance and asset management, all without the need for traditional intermediaries.\n\nAnother area of rapid innovation is the emergence of non-fungible tokens (NFTs) beyond the realm of digital art. NFTs are being used to represent ownership of real-world assets, from real estate to intellectual property, opening up new avenues for investment and fractional ownership.\n\nAs the technology matures, we're also seeing a greater focus on scalability and sustainability. Layer-2 solutions are helping to address the high gas fees and slow transaction times that have plagued many popular blockchains, while new consensus mechanisms are emerging that are more energy-efficient than their predecessors.\n\nFor anyone serious about the future of digital assets, staying informed is key. Engaging with communities and platforms that provide in-depth analysis and discussion is crucial. One such platform is [{project_name}]({project_url}), a hub for insightful crypto discussions and analysis.\n\nThe next wave of digital assets is upon us, and it's more important than ever to be part of the conversation. By understanding the trends and technologies that are shaping the future of finance, we can all be better prepared to navigate the exciting and often volatile world of cryptocurrency.\n\"\"\",\n      \"backlink_url\": project_url,\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": project_name,\n      \"image_path\": \"/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/images/kryptomoney-com.jpg\",\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Submit guest post for manual review.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.kryptomoney.com/submit-guest-post\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Submit Guest Post - Latest Crypto News\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"Submit Guest Post - Latest Crypto News advertisement [email\\xa0protected] Submit Press Release Submit Guest Post Write for Kryptomoney.com --> Submit Press Release Submit Guest Post Write for Kryptomoney.com News Bitcoin News Blockchain News Cryptocurrency News Ethereum News Exchanges News Regulations News Price Analysis Bitcoin (BTC) Analysis Et\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Dedicated submission form and guidelines for contributors working in the cryptocurrency and blockchain field.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Fill out the submission form\",\n        \"Paste the title and content\",\n        \"Upload the image\",\n        \"Submit for review\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n        \"site_url\": \"https://cryptoslate.com/directory\",\n        \"site_domain\": \"cryptoslate.com\",\n        \"type\": \"directory\",\n        \"title\": \"Coinography\",\n        \"content\": f\"Coinography is a platform for in-depth crypto discussions and analysis. We provide a space for enthusiasts and experts to connect, share insights, and explore the future of digital assets. Our mission is to foster a community dedicated to high-quality conversation and learning in the crypto space. Find us at {project_url}\",\n        \"backlink_url\": project_url,\n        \"backlink_anchor_text\": \"Coinography\",\n        \"image_path\": None,\n        \"submission_instructions\": \"Submit listing to the directory.\",\n        \"submission_url\": \"https://cryptoslate.com/directory\",\n        \"target_title\": \"Crypto Directory: Companies, Products & People | CryptoSlate\",\n        \"target_excerpt\": \"6 Open law profile Philippines SEC CASP Rules and Guidelines (2025) Effective Philippines SEC Memorandum Circular Nos. 04 and 05, Series of 2025 establish the CASP Rules and Guidelines for... Jun 8, 2026 Open law profile Vietnam Law on Digital Technology Industry: Digital-Asset Provisions Effective Vietnam’s Law 71/2025/QH15 defines digital assets,\",\n        \"opportunity_context\": \"A highly authority crypto news directory where projects and companies can be submitted for inclusion.\",\n        \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n        \"posting_action\": \"submit_listing\",\n        \"posting_steps\": [\n            \"Open the submission URL\",\n            \"Find the 'Submit a listing' or similar button\",\n            \"Fill in the required fields: Name (Coinography), Description (pasted below), URL ({project_url})\",\n            \"Submit the listing\"\n        ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://www.cryptostix.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"cryptostix.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"Beyond the Hype: Finding Real Value in Crypto\",\n      \"content\": f\"\"\"\nIn the fast-paced world of cryptocurrency, it's easy to get caught up in the hype. But for those of us who believe in the long-term potential of this technology, it's essential to look beyond the short-term price fluctuations and focus on real value. This is a common theme in the **crypto discussions** we see today.\n\nSo, how do you find the signal in the noise? It starts with a deep understanding of the underlying technology. A project with a strong use case, a dedicated development team, and a clear roadmap is always a good place to start.\n\nIt's also important to consider the community around a project. A vibrant and engaged community can be a powerful indicator of a project's health and long-term prospects.\n\nFinally, don't be afraid to do your own research. Read the whitepaper, follow the project on social media, and engage with the community. And for ongoing education and discussion, consider joining a platform like [{project_name}]({project_url}), which is dedicated to fostering in-depth conversations about the crypto space.\n\nBy focusing on real value, we can all make more informed decisions and contribute to the growth of a more mature and sustainable cryptocurrency ecosystem.\n\"\"\",\n      \"backlink_url\": project_url,\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": project_name,\n      \"image_path\": \"/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/images/cryptostix-com.jpg\",\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Submit guest post for manual review.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.cryptostix.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Write for Us: Cryptocurrency Guest Post Submission - CryptoStix.com\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"ts to us, please read our following guest posting guidelines: To write for us, your guest post must have unique contents, with good English and grammar. To write for us, your guest post must be related to cryptocurrency and Web3. Your guest post must be at least 600 words long. If your are interested in writing for us on cryptocurrency and Web3, pl\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Direct guidelines and submission instructions for crypto-focused guest posts and articles.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Follow the instructions to email the post\",\n        \"Include the title, content, and image in the email\",\n        \"Submit for review\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://icoquest.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"icoquest.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"The Evolution of Blockchain: From ICOs to IGOs\",\n      \"content\": f\"\"\"\nThe world of blockchain is constantly evolving. Just a few years ago, Initial Coin Offerings (ICOs) were all the rage. Today, we're seeing the rise of Initial Game Offerings (IGOs) and a host of other new and innovative fundraising models. This evolution is a hot topic in **crypto discussions**.\n\nThis shift reflects a broader trend in the industry: a move away from pure speculation and toward real-world utility. As the technology matures, we're seeing more and more projects that are focused on solving real-world problems and creating tangible value.\n\nOf course, with innovation comes complexity. For newcomers and seasoned investors alike, it can be challenging to keep up with the latest trends and technologies. That's why it's more important than ever to be part of a community that is dedicated to education and collaboration.\n\nPlatforms like [{project_name}]({project_url}) are playing a crucial role in this by providing a space for people to connect, share ideas, and learn from one another. By fostering a culture of open and honest discussion, these platforms are helping to build a more informed and engaged community.\n\nAs the blockchain ecosystem continues to evolve, the need for high-quality information and discussion will only grow. By embracing this, we can help to ensure that the future of blockchain is one of sustainable growth and innovation.\n\"\"\",\n      \"backlink_url\": project_url,\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": project_name,\n      \"image_path\": \"/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/images/icoquest-com.jpg\",\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Submit guest post for manual review.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://icoquest.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Write for Us: Cryptocurrency, Bitcoin, Blockchain Guest Posting Article Submission - ICOQuest.com\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"ts to us, please read our following guest posting guidelines: You guest posting article must have unique contents, with good English and grammar. Your guest posting article must be related to cryptocurrency and blockchain. Your guest post must be at least 600 words long. If your are interested in writing for us, please contact us to discuss the pos\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Active write-for-us page with clear guidelines on submitting cryptocurrency and blockchain content.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Follow the instructions to email the post\",\n        \"Include the title, content, and image in the email\",\n        \"Submit for review\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://www.cryptosdirectory.com/join\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"cryptosdirectory.com\",\n      \"type\": \"directory\",\n      \"title\": \"Coinography\",\n      \"content\": f\"A platform for high-quality crypto discussions and analysis. Join the conversation at {project_url}\",\n      \"backlink_url\": project_url,\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": \"Coinography\",\n      \"image_path\": None,\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Submit listing to the directory.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.cryptosdirectory.com/join\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Untitled\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"A curated directory specifically for cryptocurrency services, tools, and platforms.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"submit_listing\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Fill out the form with the project name, URL, and description.\",\n        \"Submit the listing\"\n      ]\n    }\n]\n\noutput = {\n    \"status\": \"ok\",\n    \"niche\": niche,\n    \"project_url\": project_url,\n    \"posts\": posts\n}\n\noutput_path = \"/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/posts.json\"\nwith open(output_path, \"w\") as f:\n    json.dump(output, f, indent=2)\n\nprint(f\"Successfully wrote {len(posts)} posts to {output_path}\")\n</execute_ipython>\nI have generated the content for all high and medium priority opportunities, including images for the guest posts, and I have made sure that every post contains the backlink. The posts have been written to `/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/posts.json`.\nI have successfully created the content for all high and medium priority backlink opportunities. Each post now correctly includes the backlink to coinography.com. I have also generated accompanying images for the guest post submissions. The final content has been written to the specified JSON file."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/posts.json","content":"{\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"niche\": \"crypto discussions\",\n  \"project_url\": \"https://coinography.com\",\n  \"posts\": [\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://www.kryptomoney.com/submit-guest-post\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"kryptomoney.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"The Future of Crypto: Navigating the Next Wave of Digital Assets\",\n      \"content\": \"\\nThe cryptocurrency landscape is in a constant state of flux. While Bitcoin and Ethereum continue to dominate headlines, a new wave of digital assets is quietly gaining momentum, promising to reshape the future of finance. For those of us deeply engaged in **crypto discussions**, it's a pivotal moment.\\n\\nOne of the most exciting developments is the rise of decentralized finance (DeFi) platforms that offer more than just trading. These platforms are building entire ecosystems of financial services, from lending and borrowing to insurance and asset management, all without the need for traditional intermediaries.\\n\\nAnother area of rapid innovation is the emergence of non-fungible tokens (NFTs) beyond the realm of digital art. NFTs are being used to represent ownership of real-world assets, from real estate to intellectual property, opening up new avenues for investment and fractional ownership.\\n\\nAs the technology matures, we're also seeing a greater focus on scalability and sustainability. Layer-2 solutions are helping to address the high gas fees and slow transaction times that have plagued many popular blockchains, while new consensus mechanisms are emerging that are more energy-efficient than their predecessors.\\n\\nFor anyone serious about the future of digital assets, staying informed is key. Engaging with communities and platforms that provide in-depth analysis and discussion is crucial. One such platform is [Coinography](https://coinography.com), a hub for insightful crypto discussions and analysis.\\n\\nThe next wave of digital assets is upon us, and it's more important than ever to be part of the conversation. By understanding the trends and technologies that are shaping the future of finance, we can all be better prepared to navigate the exciting and often volatile world of cryptocurrency.\\n\",\n      \"backlink_url\": \"https://coinography.com\",\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": \"Coinography\",\n      \"image_path\": \"/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/images/kryptomoney-com.jpg\",\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Submit guest post for manual review.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.kryptomoney.com/submit-guest-post\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Submit Guest Post - Latest Crypto News\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"Submit Guest Post - Latest Crypto News advertisement [email\\u00a0protected] Submit Press Release Submit Guest Post Write for Kryptomoney.com --> Submit Press Release Submit Guest Post Write for Kryptomoney.com News Bitcoin News Blockchain News Cryptocurrency News Ethereum News Exchanges News Regulations News Price Analysis Bitcoin (BTC) Analysis Et\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Dedicated submission form and guidelines for contributors working in the cryptocurrency and blockchain field.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Fill out the submission form\",\n        \"Paste the title and content\",\n        \"Upload the image\",\n        \"Submit for review\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://cryptoslate.com/directory\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"cryptoslate.com\",\n      \"type\": \"directory\",\n      \"title\": \"Coinography\",\n      \"content\": \"Coinography is a platform for in-depth crypto discussions and analysis. We provide a space for enthusiasts and experts to connect, share insights, and explore the future of digital assets. Our mission is to foster a community dedicated to high-quality conversation and learning in the crypto space. Find us at https://coinography.com\",\n      \"backlink_url\": \"https://coinography.com\",\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": \"Coinography\",\n      \"image_path\": null,\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Submit listing to the directory.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://cryptoslate.com/directory\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Crypto Directory: Companies, Products & People | CryptoSlate\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"6 Open law profile Philippines SEC CASP Rules and Guidelines (2025) Effective Philippines SEC Memorandum Circular Nos. 04 and 05, Series of 2025 establish the CASP Rules and Guidelines for... Jun 8, 2026 Open law profile Vietnam Law on Digital Technology Industry: Digital-Asset Provisions Effective Vietnam’s Law 71/2025/QH15 defines digital assets,\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"A highly authority crypto news directory where projects and companies can be submitted for inclusion.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"submit_listing\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Find the 'Submit a listing' or similar button\",\n        \"Fill in the required fields: Name (Coinography), Description (pasted below), URL (https://coinography.com)\",\n        \"Submit the listing\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://www.cryptostix.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"cryptostix.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"Beyond the Hype: Finding Real Value in Crypto\",\n      \"content\": \"\\nIn the fast-paced world of cryptocurrency, it's easy to get caught up in the hype. But for those of us who believe in the long-term potential of this technology, it's essential to look beyond the short-term price fluctuations and focus on real value. This is a common theme in the **crypto discussions** we see today.\\n\\nSo, how do you find the signal in the noise? It starts with a deep understanding of the underlying technology. A project with a strong use case, a dedicated development team, and a clear roadmap is always a good place to start.\\n\\nIt's also important to consider the community around a project. A vibrant and engaged community can be a powerful indicator of a project's health and long-term prospects.\\n\\nFinally, don't be afraid to do your own research. Read the whitepaper, follow the project on social media, and engage with the community. And for ongoing education and discussion, consider joining a platform like [Coinography](https://coinography.com), which is dedicated to fostering in-depth conversations about the crypto space.\\n\\nBy focusing on real value, we can all make more informed decisions and contribute to the growth of a more mature and sustainable cryptocurrency ecosystem.\\n\",\n      \"backlink_url\": \"https://coinography.com\",\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": \"Coinography\",\n      \"image_path\": \"/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/images/cryptostix-com.jpg\",\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Submit guest post for manual review.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.cryptostix.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Write for Us: Cryptocurrency Guest Post Submission - CryptoStix.com\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"ts to us, please read our following guest posting guidelines: To write for us, your guest post must have unique contents, with good English and grammar. To write for us, your guest post must be related to cryptocurrency and Web3. Your guest post must be at least 600 words long. If your are interested in writing for us on cryptocurrency and Web3, pl\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Direct guidelines and submission instructions for crypto-focused guest posts and articles.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Follow the instructions to email the post\",\n        \"Include the title, content, and image in the email\",\n        \"Submit for review\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://icoquest.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"icoquest.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"The Evolution of Blockchain: From ICOs to IGOs\",\n      \"content\": \"\\nThe world of blockchain is constantly evolving. Just a few years ago, Initial Coin Offerings (ICOs) were all the rage. Today, we're seeing the rise of Initial Game Offerings (IGOs) and a host of other new and innovative fundraising models. This evolution is a hot topic in **crypto discussions**.\\n\\nThis shift reflects a broader trend in the industry: a move away from pure speculation and toward real-world utility. As the technology matures, we're seeing more and more projects that are focused on solving real-world problems and creating tangible value.\\n\\nOf course, with innovation comes complexity. For newcomers and seasoned investors alike, it can be challenging to keep up with the latest trends and technologies. That's why it's more important than ever to be part of a community that is dedicated to education and collaboration.\\n\\nPlatforms like [Coinography](https://coinography.com) are playing a crucial role in this by providing a space for people to connect, share ideas, and learn from one another. By fostering a culture of open and honest discussion, these platforms are helping to build a more informed and engaged community.\\n\\nAs the blockchain ecosystem continues to evolve, the need for high-quality information and discussion will only grow. By embracing this, we can help to ensure that the future of blockchain is one of sustainable growth and innovation.\\n\",\n      \"backlink_url\": \"https://coinography.com\",\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": \"Coinography\",\n      \"image_path\": \"/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/images/icoquest-com.jpg\",\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Submit guest post for manual review.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://icoquest.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Write for Us: Cryptocurrency, Bitcoin, Blockchain Guest Posting Article Submission - ICOQuest.com\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"ts to us, please read our following guest posting guidelines: You guest posting article must have unique contents, with good English and grammar. Your guest posting article must be related to cryptocurrency and blockchain. Your guest post must be at least 600 words long. If your are interested in writing for us, please contact us to discuss the pos\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Active write-for-us page with clear guidelines on submitting cryptocurrency and blockchain content.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Follow the instructions to email the post\",\n        \"Include the title, content, and image in the email\",\n        \"Submit for review\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://www.cryptosdirectory.com/join\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"cryptosdirectory.com\",\n      \"type\": \"directory\",\n      \"title\": \"Coinography\",\n      \"content\": \"A platform for high-quality crypto discussions and analysis. Join the conversation at https://coinography.com\",\n      \"backlink_url\": \"https://coinography.com\",\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": \"Coinography\",\n      \"image_path\": null,\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Submit listing to the directory.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.cryptosdirectory.com/join\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Untitled\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"A curated directory specifically for cryptocurrency services, tools, and platforms.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"submit_listing\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Fill out the form with the project name, URL, and description.\",\n        \"Submit the listing\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-bifrost","model":"gemini-2.5-pro","usage":{"input":9955,"output":5887,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15842,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780985405017,"responseId":"PK4natLhAtOD694Pl52y-Qg"}}
